Title: Magento Security enhancements that help close RCE,XSS,CSRF and other vulnerabilities
Description: SUPEE-10975, Magento Commerce 1.14.4.0 and Open Source 1.9.4.0 contain multiple security enhancements that help close remote code execution (RCE), cross-site scripting (XSS), cross-site request forgery (CSRF) and other vulnerabilities.
NotImpacted: All versions before 1.5.0.0, all versions starting from 1.9.4.0
